// ============================================================================
// WHAT THIS DOES (generic):
//   - Imports a monthly payroll/roster export into a single "master" sheet.
//   - Assigns each person a Group + Group Lead using a configurable mapping.
//   - Reads a pre-built summary sheet to render a lightweight cost dashboard.
//   - Optionally calls the Anthropic API for narrative insights.
//
// EVERYTHING environment-specific (API key, sheet/tab names, optional source
// URL) is entered ONCE through the "⚙️ Setup" menu and stored in Script
// Properties. No secrets, IDs, or company data live in this file.
//
// NOTE ON SCHEMA: The import schema below is a DELIBERATELY SIMPLIFIED,
// SYNTHETIC EXAMPLE. The original author works with confidential HR data and
// cannot publish the production column mapping. Replace SCHEMA + mappings with
// your own before use.
